{"tid":2328083,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又唔係柒婆死，只係上手低級打手死，使唔使搞到咁大件事！","createTime":"2020-12-16T11:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T03:38:28.000Z","uid":329842,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3e0a952d4094649be42332f98f2cea61e56d634e","tid":2328083,"uid":329842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:05:04.000Z","msg":"件事幾值得講啊？雖要開咁多post去講咩？<br />\n只係死左一件上手留落黎嘅低級打手<br />\n連一個柒婆不屑一顧的人<br />\n明白各位開心，我自己都開心<br />\n但未至於去到要洗版囉！<br />\n集中係同一個post講唔得嘅？<br />\n每個人諗到樣野就開post<br />\n特別係啲on9扮正經嘅標題<br />\n不論開post嘅動機係乜嘢<br />\n成件事弱智兼冇腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">死嘅只係上手留低嘅低級打手<br />\n佢個名唔配係連登標題出現</span></span>"},{"pid":"b5696a8180dfbc3f04cea35673e1126149b33c00","tid":2328083,"uid":329842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03aac07825c1b4e15c350957634b31b695185f0","tid":2328083,"uid":329842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:09:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207d012e66d5da6ab08a9e6d022a42828e8efe9c","tid":2328083,"uid":329842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:11:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad8b701e919a2fa6414ac1789eddcfac5dd1892","tid":2328083,"uid":329842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c8098203fdb25d2ef4a773f873295de5068d86","tid":2328083,"uid":